attacks:
- which squares are "open to attack"? (unoccupied surrounding a particular square X)
- am i adjacent to any enemies? find all of them

pathing:
- is square Y reachable from square X?  or is it blocked?  (given a grid of squares that are either blocked or not)
- if it's reachable, then how many steps does it take to get there (no diagonal steps allowed)

turn order
- sort by row, then by column

terrain grid
list of goblins
list of elves

taking turns:
- order units in reading order
- if not in range of any enemies, then try to move in range to array
- if in range, then attack.

